"title": "5591: treasure",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5591: treasure",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Highly valued objects or accumulated riches. Treasure has at best only short-term benefit but can bring spiritual dangers. Spiritual treasure is of eternal value and comes from knowing and serving God.</p>\n<h2>The limitations of accumulated treasure</h2>\n<h3>It is easily lost</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:11\">ISA 64:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:13\">2KI 24:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:13\">JER 15:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:3\">JER 17:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:5\">JER 20:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:10-Lam1:11\">LAM 1:10–1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:15\">HOS 13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:6\">OBA 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19\">MAT 6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:2-Jas5:3\">JAS 5:2–5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:14\">REV 18:14</a></p>\n<h3>It is no security against God's displeasure</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:4\">PRO 11:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:20\">JOB 20:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:13\">JER 51:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:19\">EZK 7:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:6\">HOS 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:18\">ZEP 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:16–12:21</a></p>\n<h3>It does not satisfy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:10\">ECC 5:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:6\">PSA 39:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:6\">HAG 1:6</a></p>\n<h2>The spiritual dangers of accumulated treasure</h2>\n<h3>It can lead to pride</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:13-Deut8:14\">DEU 8:13–8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:20\">EZK 7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:4-Ezek28:5\">EZK 28:4–28:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:30\">DAN 4:30</a></p>\n<h3>It can lead a person away from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17\">REV 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:24-Job31:25\">JOB 31:24–31:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:28\">JOB 31:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:28\">PRO 11:28</a></p>\n<h3>It can lead to greed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:15\">LUK 12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:9-1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:9–6:10</a></p>\n<h3>Acquiring it can lead to dishonesty</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:21\">JOS 7:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:10\">PSA 62:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:6\">PRO 21:6</a></p>\n<h3>It can lead to idolatry</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:2-Exod32:4\">EXO 32:2–32:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:7-Isa2:8\">ISA 2:7–2:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:20\">EZK 7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:17\">EZK 16:17</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual treasure</h2>\n<h3>Treasure consists in knowing God and his wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2-Col2:3\">COL 2:2–2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:12-Job28:19\">JOB 28:12–28:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:4\">PRO 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:13-Prov3:15\">PRO 3:13–3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:10-Prov8:11\">PRO 8:10–8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:3-Prov24:4\">PRO 24:3–24:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:6\">ISA 33:6</a></p>\n<h3>God's word is supreme treasure</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:12\">JOB 23:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:9-Ps19:10\">PSA 19:9–19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:72\">PSA 119:72</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:127\">PSA 119:127</a></p>\n<h3>The kingdom of God is supreme treasure</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:44\">MAT 13:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:45-Matt13:46\">MAT 13:45–13:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:52\">MAT 13:52</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual treasure is more important than material possessions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:26\">HEB 11:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:23-Job22:25\">JOB 22:23–22:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:44-Matt13:46\">MAT 13:44–13:46</a></p>\n<h3>It is of eternal value</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:33\">LUK 12:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:20\">MAT 6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:4\">1PE 1:4</a></p>\n<h3>It is gained through generosity and wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21\">MAT 19:21</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:21\">MRK 10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:22\">LUK 18:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:21\">PRO 8:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:6\">PRO 15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:18-1Tim6:19\">1TI 6:18–6:19</a></p>\n<h2>Treasure reveals true commitment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:21\">MAT 6:21</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:34\">LUK 12:34</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:24\">MAT 6:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:13\">LUK 16:13</a></p>\n<h2>Believers willingly give God their treasures</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:11\">MAT 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:22\">EXO 35:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:24\">JOS 6:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:3-1Chr29:5\">1CH 29:3–29:5</a></p>\n<h2>God's people are his treasured possession</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:6\">DEU 7:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:5\">EXO 19:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:2\">DEU 14:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:18\">DEU 26:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:4\">PSA 135:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:17\">MAL 3:17</a></p>\n<h2>The gospel as treasure in clay jars</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:7\">2CO 4:7</a></p>",
